s of Tolkien, Beowulf, and Harry Potter.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aLatin poetry, Medieval and modernzEnglandvTranslations into English. 0aMiddle AgesvPoetry. 0aRiddles, LatinzEnglandvTranslations into English. 7aHISTORY / Ancient / General.2bisacsh1 aA.M., Juster.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311060681240uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978144262529740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781442625297423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781442625297.jpg  a978-3-11-060681-2  University of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles